By exploring strategy, mission, and innovation and how they interact, this course will teach you how to help your organization disrupt itself before anyone else does. Develop the knowledge and skills necessary to lead a more agile organization and respond successfully to change in customers during increasingly disruptive times. Uncover your business' ability to act on a more human mission for the company, doing good while also doing well.
